_sText:
surf_voteforthisone
==================

A tier 3 surf map with 8 stages and 2 bonuses. ------------------

I have been working on this map for the past several months, and it's finally ready for release.


The Specs

  • Easy Tier 3
  • 8 Stages
  • 2 Bonuses

The mappers (by stage)

  1. FalseLogic
  2. Krazy
  3. FalseLogic
  4. Falc
  5. FalseLogic
  6. FalseLogic
  7. Juxtapo
  8. Malt

Bonus Stages:

  1. Juxtapo
  2. Furchee

For the bonuses, I request that any surf-timer server that plays this map to not allow teleporting to bonus with commands. There are entrances to both bonuses on the map.

More screenshots are available here


The zones (for surftimers) are as follows:

  • Stage 1 - stage1
  • Stage 2 - stage2
  • Stage 3 - stage3
  • Stage 4 - stage4
  • Stage 5 - stage5
  • Stage 6 - stage6
  • Stage 7 - stage7
  • Stage 8 - stage8
  • End of map - map_end
  • Bonus 1 Start - bonus1
  • Bonus 1 end - bonus1_end
  • Bonus 2 Start - bonus2
  • Bonus 2 End - bonus2_end
